- [x] Repository pattern (UserRepository via dbStrategy, SecurityRepository)
- [x] Security repository (bcrypt hashing + access/refresh JWT signing + verification)
- [x] Winston logging system (console + file transports, colorized levels)
- [x] Middleware pipeline (tracer, injectServices, validation, auth, errorHandler)
- [x] Docker multi-stage build + Docker Compose (dev, test, prod)
- [x] Socket.IO integration (connection/disconnect logging)
- [x] Helmet + express-rate-limit + CORS security configuration
- [x] **Database strategy** — MongoStrategy (full Mongoose wrapper implementation)
- [x] **Storage strategy** — LocalStorageStrategy (full filesystem implementation)
- [x] **Strategy stubs** — PostgresStrategy + S3StorageStrategy (same interface, throw not-implemented)
- [x] **Model auto-loader** — `src/models/index.js` scans directory, registers all models automatically
- [x] Fixed `.env` typo (`prodcution` → `production`)

